
Notes about porting considerations
__________________________________

$Id: Porting,v 1.1.1.1 2000/11/01 03:06:58 turner Exp $

Need to know:

- command to invoke F90 compiler
- F90 options for debugging, optimization, listing, etc.
- result of uname -a
- suffix used for module info files
- suffix used for list files
- how the vendor's cpp works
- compile flag for specifying location of module info files
- routine for CPU time (see Clock.F90)
- routine for flushing logical unit buffer (see FlushUnit.F90)
- routine for grabbing command-line args (see ParseArg.F90)
- details about internal I/O (see ParseArg.F90)
